data.description: Welcome to your own slice of paradise! Nestled on 4.4 acres, this property offers a delightful blend of meadow, trees, and a seasonal wetland providing a perfect blend of nature and serenity. No zoning, year-round access, electric to neighboring property, well and septic approved. Located just 15 minutes away from the charming town of Whitefish, Montana, this property offers easy access to a wide range of amenities, including shopping, dining, skiing, and entertainment. The privacy of this property offers a tranquil escape from the hustle and bustle of daily life, making it an ideal place to relax and unwind. Contact Jacquelyn Hupp @ (406) 360-2869 or your real estate professional. Located an hour from Glacier National Park, one of the most stunning and pristine wilderness areas in the world where you can enjoy hiking, camping, fishing, and wildlife viewing.  Purchase neighboring lot MLS 30006680 for twice the acreage!
